{"tid":596340,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[撞車失憶]撞到人地車側邊，係咪我唔啱？","createTime":"2018-03-17T14:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T13:15:22.000Z","uid":70215,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"bdf80ffe1772a8488b35c459508c2f2e6a29bbe2","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:04:30.000Z","msg":"今日行錯路，兜左入南灣路<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/214733_f2ab2aa7b20270ac7d2f28a56152ac2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F214733_f2ab2aa7b20270ac7d2f28a56152ac2e.png&h=53ee0da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n向住倔頭路既方向行緊<br />\n大概去到依個位<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/215011_ffdb5d2673d42d933b54596b634905db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F215011_ffdb5d2673d42d933b54596b634905db.png&h=6bcfdd98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有架車係白色貨VAN個位唔知倒車定從右線轉右入錶位（失憶）<br />\n總之就撞到架車既左前方凹咗<br />\n對方因為係外國人，架車又唔係佢<br />\n所以冇即時報價<br />\n因為第一次撞車，所以嗰時好慌張就打咗999<br />\n對方就不斷話係我責任<br />\n但係當我靜落嚟嘅時候<br />\n我明明行緊正線，佢倒車定從右線轉右入錶位都要係安全情況下先做到<br />\n加上我一出灣係依個位已經係大直路，佢應該睇到我<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/220105_369c0397b26d990b9460b926f1614a62.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F220105_369c0397b26d990b9460b926f1614a62.png&h=edc34120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果和解想賠小啲，依個係咪理據？<br />\n和解唔到，上庭勝算有幾大？<br />\n利伸：雙方無CAM<br />\n事後有道歉，因為嚇親佢車上啲小朋友，但係無回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b27340b9cf65028eff033c0d1426474e963862","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:07:31.000Z","msg":"我仲讀緊書，只係想大事化小，因為我撞凹左人地兩道門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b86fa460694b85ff5788a5ea353dc390e76a489","tid":596340,"uid":154174,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"你無影低當時的情況？差佬黎到又點講？"},{"pid":"536d80e861e27bc3cbe8b9cc0ce1ae1acfca7657","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"7b86fa460694b85ff5788a5ea353dc390e76a489","tid":596340,"uid":154174,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"你無影低當時的情況？差佬黎到又點講？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:12:44.000Z","msg":"都係循例抄低雙方資料然後建議和解，比左個number<br />\n我地雙方都冇影相<br />\n我只有影低兩部車既損傷"},{"pid":"6419f1217271c2e75e0763cbe4931efe0d19b5c2","tid":596340,"uid":83411,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:23:46.000Z","msg":"一，可拖則拖，鬼佬未必知十四日內要去搵警察落口供，到時可當和解<br />\n<br />\n二，人地屬小路出大路，但係你撞人門位，佢未必輸得晒，如果你本身車要用保險claim 整車，就一定報警"},{"pid":"dcaa29ceb532d773e94fd144411339dafb517ed9","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6419f1217271c2e75e0763cbe4931efe0d19b5c2","tid":596340,"uid":83411,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:23:46.000Z","msg":"一，可拖則拖，鬼佬未必知十四日內要去搵警察落口供，到時可當和解<br />\n<br />\n二，人地屬小路出大路，但係你撞人門位，佢未必輸得晒，如果你本身車要用保險claim 整車，就一定報警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:30:20.000Z","msg":"即係50/50，雙方都有責任？<br />\n對方係女人，我一講到佢其實都有責任就起曬鋼"},{"pid":"1aa7f065b1d63e51d2bf92ec382905cce866ec53","tid":596340,"uid":72751,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:35:51.000Z","msg":"連人地點行你都講唔出 叫個官點信你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f9d67ad4b1b116a333274f3c968a00590d9d8a","tid":596340,"uid":40052,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:43:57.000Z","msg":"失憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你魂魄番齊先上來講野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c594c1d69c012cff1f3475ac86ca2d2406aeb416","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1aa7f065b1d63e51d2bf92