/>\n都知佢做左一啲野BLOCK左我條路我煞唔切先炒<br />\n唔通佢明明阻住我比油撞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:15:18.000Z","msg":"撞得車腰即係佢當時都出左一半啦？<br />\n你離遠都見唔到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:07:54.000Z","msg":"比你提一提，係右邊線入，因為都係預計唔到既野先會炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e372f35e7c617814927b01dfc4469e01b2564a44","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f8196872a97d39bca0ca6202a514aa4c46ea0d0","tid":596340,"uid":6777,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:54:01.000Z","msg":"和解算啦<br />\n7下7下咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:09:10.000Z","msg":"我都想，但係件事始終雙方有責任，而依家對家唔想負任何責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a2ce3f6b5913e26f15dcf71c1fc1869142ca6e","tid":596340,"uid":27251,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:14:56.000Z","msg":"你咩都唔撚知就唔好揸車出街，點會唔知前方有架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16698c3b6c7b22e59abcb31e2a89b513a139422","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74a2ce3f6b5913e26f15dcf71c1fc1869142ca6e","tid":596340,"uid":27251,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:14:56.000Z","msg":"你咩都唔撚知就唔好揸車出街，點會唔知前方有架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:18:03.000Z","msg":"右線CUT入黎想入錶位，唔係係自己條線"},{"pid":"c985cd5a660202cd505649a3c4cb6846d4e64450","tid":596340,"uid":79481,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:44:05.000Z","msg":"無cam真係50/50<br />\n<br />\n尤其是你撞到佢條腰<br />\n<br />\n可以估計架車應該已經轉左 踩住條線一段時間<br />\n<br />\n加上佢架車上面有細路<br />\n<br />\n個官應該唔會覺得個阿爸會好快咁甩入黎然後俾你撞腰<br />\n<br />\n如果我係官 應該會判你無留意交通情況食曬"},{"pid":"8fad60686f9f20619786d8cebac3b326d38dddff","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"c985cd5a660202cd505649a3c4cb6846d4e64450","tid":596340,"uid":79481,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:44:05.000Z","msg":"無cam真係50/50<br />\n<br />\n尤其是你撞到佢條腰<br />\n<br />\n可以估計架車應該已經轉左 踩住條線一段時間<br />\n<br />\n加上佢架車上面有細路<br />\n<br />\n個官應該唔會覺得個阿爸會好快咁甩入黎然後俾你撞腰<br />\n<br />\n如果我係官 應該會判你無留意交通情況食曬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/025916_88d8ef23db815e2245f1abd10b4ba4a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F025916_88d8ef23db815e2245f1abd10b4ba4a1.png&h=68cef51f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大概前轆對上 未到中間"},{"pid":"b9fe3d47244ee44c4882a84f6c11de1b3aef6d04","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T19:07:33.000Z","msg":"補充返，佢突然右轉block左條路，係我煞唔切撞埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係佢係低估我既速度先轉右<br />\n咁樣唔係大家都有責任咩<br />\n加上佢話自己有打燈<br />\n但係我當刻睇唔到佢有打到"},{"pid":"35bb49530f22cc8dce628b6a239ecb29b1087408","tid":596340,"uid":79481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8fad60686f9f20619786d8cebac3b326d38dddff","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"c985cd5a660202cd505649a3c4cb6846d4e64450","tid":596340,"uid":79481,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:44:05.000Z","msg":"無cam真係50/50<br />\n<br />\n尤其是你撞到佢條腰<br />\n<br />\n可以估計架車應該已經轉左 踩住條線一段時間<br />\n<br />\n加上佢架車上面有細路<br />\n<br />\n個官應該唔會覺得個阿爸會好快咁甩入黎然後俾你撞腰<br />\n<br />\n如果我係官 應該會判你無留意交通情況食曬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/025916_88d8ef23db815e2245f1abd10b4ba4a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F025916_88d8ef23db815e2245f1abd10b4ba4a1.png&h=68cef51f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大概前轆對上 未到中間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T19:49:09.000Z","msg":"點阿 撞腰定撞車頭阿"},{"pid":"20d0188fb307f80601e0a977e3a7729e4c738a82","tid":596340,"uid":79481,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b9fe3d47244ee44c4882a84f6c11de1b3aef6d04","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T19:07:33.000Z","msg":"補充返，佢突然右轉block左條路，係我煞唔切撞埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係佢係低估我既速度先轉右<br />\n咁樣唔係大家都有責任咩<br />\n加上佢話自己有打燈<br />\n但係我當刻睇唔到佢有打到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T19:50:23.000Z","msg":"如果係佢突然切入黎就係佢唔岩<br />\n<br />\n但你講到咁唔肯定 d口供改左幾廿次<br />\n<br />\n我係官都信你唔過wor"},{"pid":"89f4fbce6b5e9eec8b2affbbabd8a0f358830d2c","tid":596340,"uid":128210,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T19:58:49.000Z","msg":"點睇都係你錯：<br />\n1. 倒車出緊，撞到車前半個位，代表佢左 半架車身。你咁都睇唔到？<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪撚駕駛車出街 ， ok ?</span><br />\n<br />\n2佢係右線轉右泊緊車，你撞佢左前方。代表佢已經轉左右 。<br />\n（如果你先係正確方，你應該撞到佢車頭。）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">跪求巴打唔好駕駛車出街。好嗎？</span>"},{"pid":"1665861cf28708b6bb00f58086cc38305caba3e8","tid":596340,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T20:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇都係你錯：<br />\n1. 倒車出緊，撞到車前半個位，代表佢 出 左 半架車身。你咁都睇唔到？<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪撚駕駛車出街 ， ok ?</span><br />\n<br />\n2佢係右線轉右泊緊車，你撞佢左前方。代表佢已經轉左右 。<br />\n（如果你先係正確方，你應該撞到佢車頭。）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">跪求巴打唔好駕駛車出街。好嗎？</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係1. 的情況，如果你係正確的一邊。係正常情況會人地車尾撞到你車頭。<br />\n<br />\n而家你撞落人車身，係你無留意到人地已經倒後左。<br />\n<br />\n駕駛經驗有無2年？<br />\n咁的路行幾多？<br />\n咁都停唔切？"},{"pid":"efa8bdf31633aac2370eaafd0d8ffdf7a175a902","tid":596340,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T20:05:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無cam真係50/50<br />\n<br />\n尤其是你撞到佢條腰<br />\n<br />\n可以估計架車應該已經轉左 踩住條線一段時間<br />\n<br />\n加上佢架車上面有細路<br />\n<br />\n個官應該唔會覺得個阿爸會好快咁甩入黎然後俾你撞腰<br />\n<br />\n如果我係官 應該會判你無留意交通情況食曬</blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/025916_88d8ef23db815e2245f1abd10b4ba4a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F025916_88d8ef23db815e2245f1abd10b4ba4a1.png&h=68cef51f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大概前轆對上 未到中間</blockquote>點阿 撞腰定撞車頭阿</blockquote><br />\n又話撞人2隻門。<br />\n2隻門又點車頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nE個年代竟然有人車無cam 。"},{"pid":"d566f2c5f5b5dc165fe728c8be2899e815afdf10","tid":596340,"uid":136735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T20:06:28.000Z","msg":"又唔記得又唔肯定　想點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78668411a765016ba500dd49b4dcec70ec247f5","tid":596340,"uid":105155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T23:19:41.000Z","msg":"屌，我係官都判你錯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 表達到1999咁"},{"pid":"79f3eafee59bc6ad237538aff456c36746814384","tid":596340,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e78668411a765016ba500dd49b4dcec70ec247f5","tid":596340,"uid":105155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T23:19:41.000Z","msg":"屌，我係官都判你錯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 表達到1999咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n到呢刻樓豬都仲未表達得好清楚<br />\n<br />\n但就理直氣壯話雙方有責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 倒車正常都要睇到有無車啦，點解會覺得人地係行過黎比你撞腰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好離奇"},{"pid":"f20fec1819eb5e12b28fbd1459773d206040efd3","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"s