>\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過無cam,  兩個都告老不機會大, 對面如果堅持淨係你責任，唯有由個官判"},{"pid":"270f863698fafc30b056cffb7d0dd61b791f8010","tid":596340,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"hit and run 有咁快走咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a07ef0a674c47a9ccc6c8b78195e7ca8ace317d","tid":596340,"uid":17159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T04:11:03.000Z","msg":"佢前碌同尾碌喺撞嘅時候大概各自喺邊個位？"},{"pid":"b3495a3de56f96cf20a7b2a54f055bb87680ce51","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"133f2240792474d077a52ae28c9876f33d01e359","tid":596340,"uid":53520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T04:02:22.000Z","msg":"睇番樓主咁多回憶<br />\n<br />\n樓主的記憶之中的事實<br />\n<br />\n1 樓主速度唔高50左右，轉出灣直路都仍然見到架大霸係對面線 (無打方向燈)<br />\n<br />\n2 到樓主繼續直行左一段距離，架大霸突然扭出轉右入去錶位 (無打方向燈)<br />\n<br />\n3 樓主盡brake 但都停唔到，先撞到車頭碌對上少少位置，由於擺橫左架車，拉花埋第二道門<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果上面係事實，我撐樓主<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過無cam,  兩個都告老不機會大, 對面如果堅持淨係你責任，唯有由個官判"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T04:11:06.000Z","msg":"多謝幫忙綜合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d17853a8447f8b74958ae76ed0b9de19e3fa48","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a07ef0a674c47a9ccc6c8b78195e7ca8ace317d","tid":596340,"uid":17159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T04:11:03.000Z","msg":"佢前碌同尾碌喺撞嘅時候大概各自喺邊個位？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T04:27:23.000Z","msg":"前面入左我條線 後轆仲係對面線"},{"pid":"a2d84efb2aa223c0d779e267ace90105d0c1ebf0","tid":596340,"uid":42293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d2d17853a8447f8b74958ae76ed0b9de19e3fa48","tid":596340,"uid":70215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a07ef0a674c47a9ccc6c8b78195e7ca8ace317d","tid":596340,"uid":17159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"